text: Franz Haupert (27 October 1907 - 30 June 1996) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Käerjeng
